      "content": "hey quick question. im taking sertraline for my mood but finals week is coming up and i feel super low and drained. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help boost my energy/mood naturally since the sertraline feels a bit slow. is that cool to mix or is it gonna be an issue?",
