    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh man, serotonin syndrome sounds scary. but i read online that because St. Johns Wort is just a herbal supplement it doesnt work the same way as pharmaceuticals, so it shouldn't be that intense? i feel like i can manage it if i just take a lower dose of the supplement. like, if i just take a small amount, is it still that risky?",
