      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get being cautious but honestly my doctor is super hard to reach and i really cant wait weeks for an appointment while i'm struggling like this. plus, i've seen people on forums say it's fine as long as you don't take the max dose. if i just took half a tablet of the supplement once a day, would that actually be a problem or are you just being extra careful? like, is there really any way it could be life threatening if it's just a tiny bit?",
